com.radixdlt.client.core.atoms

Class Atom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.radix.serialization2.client.SerializableObject
      • com.radixdlt.client.core.atoms.Atom

  • @SerializerId2(value="radix.atom")
public final class Atom
extends SerializableObject
    An atom is the fundamental atomic unit of storage on the ledger (similar to a block in a blockchain) and defines the actions that can be issued onto the ledger.
